          <td height="10">
		  <p><a href="../index.html" class="breadcrumb">Club Penguin Help</a> &gt; The Stage<span class="lg_title"><img src="images/stage-2.gif" width="350" height="220" align="right" /></span></p>
		  <p class="lg_title">The Stage</p>
          <p class="style1"><a name="auditions" id="auditions"></a>&quot;Where are the auditions for the show at The Stage?</p>
          <p>Billybob posted in the 'What's New' blog that The Stage  is a great new way to use your creativity.&nbsp;  This means you can set up auditions with your buddies to decide who will  play which part and then rehearse and perform the skit. You could host  auditions in your igloo or at The Stage.</p>
          <p class="style1"><br />
              <strong><a name="shows" id="shows"></a>Are there going to be different shows at The Stage?&nbsp; If so, when?</strong></p>
          <p>Absolutely! In the future, there will be different shows  to participate in and watch at The Stage.&nbsp;  When and how often these themes will arrive at The Stage is unknown.  Check The Stage billboard on the outside of the building and remember to read  the Club Penguin Times newspaper for upcoming show info.</p>
          <p><span class="style1"><a name="costumes" id="costumes"></a>How do I join the the play if I can't buy the costumes?</strong></span><span class="blue_title"><span class="lg_title"><img src="images/stage-1.gif" width="350" height="220" align="right" /></span></span></p>
          <p>There are lots of great ways you can participate in the  Penguins in Space play even if you can't buy any costumes.&nbsp; Everyone can use the script and if you&rsquo;ve  been around Club Penguin for a while, use some of the fun free items you&rsquo;ve  collected from past parties and special events to create your own character for  the play. Being an actor on the stage isn&rsquo;t the only important role at The  Stage. Every theatrical performance needs an enthusiastic audience, ushers,  ticket collectors, servers and more. Use your imagination to create your own  role and have fun!</p>
          <p class="style1"><a name="stay" id="stay"></a>Will The Stage always be here?</p>
          <p>The Stage is a new building in Club Penguin and is here  to stay.&nbsp; For as long as it is enjoyed by  players, it will continue to be a fun and imaginative place to play with friends  in Club Penguin.</p>
          <p>&nbsp;</p>
			<p>&nbsp;</p>			</td>
